# Add to Cart

## Add a product from the PDP to the Cart

* Go to the home page
* Click on the Products tab in the main menu - The sub menu should open with the tabs for product 
categories
* Click on the 'writing Instrument' Category - User should redirect to the category landing page of 
the products of a specific category
* Click on the any "available" product (tile) - The PDP for the corresponding product should open
* Click on the "Add to cart" in the buy box on PDP - The product should be added to the user's 
shippoing cart
* User should be able to view the total number of products through the counter on Cart Button in 
the header


